blog.name: garlic-bread-stans
blog.title: The Garlic Bread Stans
blog.description:
ASKS AND FANFIC REQUESTS ARE WIDE OPEN!!!!!!!!!!

Welcome fellow believers...

You have reached your home world, a place that all fandoms call home.

Multi Admin!

~Soup-Stan~

Just a struggling writer who is in way too many fandoms... I’m also a walking disaster

Apple-Stan

I'm just an eccentric girl who is tragically and irrevocably in love with far too many fictional characters, who are the reason she's going to be alone for the rest of her life.

In other words, they have ruined men for me.

My biggest dream is to live in a world where Marvel is real and my apples are always perfect...and Infinity War was three hours of Loki proclaiming his undying love for me...

Carbohydrate-Stan

Literally just a failure with a love for carbohydrates, Brendon Boyd Urie and Lady Gaga as well as writing stories in my head. *whispers* I have double-jointed toes. Ryden was real and you can fight me on that if you desire to.

🚨WARNING🚨

May experience extreme fangirling, breathlessness, fits of tears and the occasional collapsing fit. Unfortunately, no Garlic-Bread-Stans are responsible so enter at your own risk...

You made it this far...so get ready...bring popcorn and ENJOY!!!!

body:
Killer

Her hands shook uncontrollably as sobs wracked her body. She could not even begin to comprehend what she had done. Blood soaked her shirt, plagued her skin and she could not scrub it off.

His blood.

That which minutes ago ran through his veins, was quite literally on her hands.

And the worst part was, she would do it again.

In a heartbeat, in order to protect her people.

Because leadership, is sacrifice.
